OL,3,CMan who stabbed wife to death as she
OL,4,Cpushed pram in street jailed
OL,6,FJudge Mr Justice Cotter sentences
OL,7,FHabibur Masum to life in prison
OL,9,FA "violent, self-centred, jealous,
OL,10,Fcontrolling and coercive" man who
OL,11,Fstalked his estranged wife before
OL,12,Fstabbing her to death as she pushed
OL,13,Ftheir baby in a pram in the street has
OL,14,Fbeen jailed for at least 28 years.
OL,16,FHabibur Masum, 26, launched a
OL,17,F"ferocious" attack on 27-year-old
OL,18,FKulsuma Akter as she walked on
OL,19,FWestgate in Bradford, before calmly
OL,20,Fleaving their seven-month-old son at
OL,21,Fthe scene and going on the run.
