OL,3,CMan who stabbed wife to death as she
OL,4,Cpushed pram in street jailed
OL,6,FA trial at Bradford Crown Court heard
OL,7,Fthat Masum murdered Ms Akter after
OL,8,Ftracking her to a refuge, where she
OL,9,Fhad been staying to escape his abuse.
OL,11,FHe stabbed her 26 times and stamped on
OL,12,Fher as she lay on the ground.
OL,14,FJailing him for life with a minimum
OL,15,Fterm of 28 years, Judge Mr Justice
OL,16,FCotter told Masum: "I'm sure that you
OL,17,Fcan be properly described as violent,
OL,18,Fself-centred, jealous, controlling and
OL,19,Fcoercive with a firmly held view your
OL,20,Fwife was not your equal.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/11
