OL,3,CMan who stabbed wife to death as she
OL,4,Cpushed pram in street jailed
OL,6,F"You stole a precious young life in a
OL,7,Fbrutal and merciless fashion. It was
OL,8,Fyour refusal of her to have a life
OL,9,Ffree from your violence and
OL,10,Fcontrolling behaviour. You have shown
OL,11,Fno real remorse, only self pity."
OL,13,FMasum's trial heard his wife had left
OL,14,Fhim after prolonged abuse, culminating
OL,15,Fin an incident where he held a knife
OL,16,Fto her throat following an assault at
OL,17,Ftheir home in Oldham in November 2023.
