OL,3,CMan who stabbed wife to death as she
OL,4,Cpushed pram in street jailed
OL,6,FAfter finding her through her phone
OL,7,Flocation, Masum, originally from
OL,8,FBangladesh, was seen on CCTV in the
OL,9,Fdays leading up to the fatal attack
OL,10,F"loitering, watching and waiting" in
OL,11,Fstreets around the hostel, jurors
OL,12,Fheard.
OL,14,FHe sent her a photo of the front of
OL,15,Fthe building with a message saying: "I
OL,16,Fknow that you are living in this
OL,17,Fplace. I knew from the first day you
OL,18,Fmoved here."
