OL,3,CMan who stabbed wife to death as she
OL,4,Cpushed pram in street jailed
OL,6,FHe sent her messages threatening to
OL,7,Fkill her family members if she did not
OL,8,Freturn to him, before trying to lure
OL,9,Fher out by sending her fake messages
OL,10,Ffrom a local GP practice pretending
OL,11,Ftheir son had an appointment.
OL,13,FThe court heard Ms Akter eventually
OL,14,Ffelt safe enough to leave the refuge
OL,15,Fon 6 April last year after Masum
OL,16,Fupdated his social media falsely
OL,17,Fclaiming to be in Spain.
OL,19,FAs she was walking in the city centre
OL,20,Fwith a friend, pushing her baby in a
OL,21,Fpram, Masum confronted her.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/11
