OL,3,CMan who stabbed wife to death as she
OL,4,Cpushed pram in street jailed
OL,6,FHe admitted manslaughter and
OL,7,Fpossession of a knife but denied
OL,8,Fmurder.
OL,10,FIn victim personal statements read in
OL,11,Fcourt, Ms Akter's family said they
OL,12,Fwere worried about what Masum would do
OL,13,Fto her before the murder.
OL,15,FHer brother, Imran, said: "He was
OL,16,Fconstantly trying to speak to her and
OL,17,Fcontrol her actions and she felt she
OL,18,Fhad to go somewhere he did not know...
OL,19,FShe had gone through so much and still
OL,20,Fwas but was being so strong and I was
OL,21,Fso proud of her for that.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G7/11
