OL,3,CMan who stabbed wife to death as she
OL,4,Cpushed pram in street jailed
OL,6,F"My main worry was he could kill her
OL,7,Fand leave (the baby) alone to escape.
OL,8,FThis is almost what he did - leaving
OL,9,Fher alone, dead in the street with
OL,10,F(the baby) alone... I still cannot
OL,11,Fcomprehend this happened to my baby
OL,12,Fsister."
OL,14,FHe added: "She did not deserve to be
OL,15,Frobbed of seeing (her son's)
OL,16,Fmilestones. She did not deserve to be
OL,17,Frobbed of life. This for us will be a
OL,18,Flife sentence. Life is so precious.
OL,19,F(Her son) is the only light in all of
OL,20,Fthis darkness."
