OL,6,F'A monster whose name does not deserve
OL,7,Fto be mentioned'
OL,9,FIn a statement issued after the
OL,10,Fsentencing, Ms Akter's family said her
OL,11,Floss had left "a gaping hole in the
OL,12,Flives of all her family and friends".
OL,14,FIt added: "We have been left with a
OL,15,Fprofound sense of emptiness and a deep
OL,16,Fand painful void in our lives. She was
OL,17,Fa loving, caring and kind soul with a
OL,18,Fgenerous nature and touched the lives
OL,19,Fof everyone she came into contact with.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G9/11
