OL,3,CMan who stabbed wife to death as she
OL,4,Cpushed pram in street jailed
OL,6,F"As a family we miss her beautiful
OL,7,Fsmile which would light up any room
OL,8,Fshe entered. We will miss her humour,
OL,9,Fher kindness and her love.
OL,11,F"We will never forgive the monster who
OL,12,Ftook Kulsuma from us and we do not
OL,13,Fwish to utter his name. It does not
OL,14,Fdeserve to be mentioned. The monster
OL,15,Fwho savagely took Kulsuma from not
OL,16,Fonly us, but also from her baby son.
OL,17,FHe will never know her beauty and her
OL,18,Fkindness.
